you require.",{"label":85,"content":86},"Is there a limit to the number of projects I can open with you?","We focus on one comprehensive project at a time, which can encompass multiple services or solutions. For example, an AI chatbot with website development and integration. This approach ensures we maintain high work quality and allows us to complete your project faster by dedicating our full attention and resources to it.",{"label":88,"content":89},"How does the membership pause feature operate?","The pause feature is designed for your convenience. Once we deliver a project and you don't have additional work for a week or a month, you can pause your membership and resume it whenever you're ready. We operate on a monthly billing cycle with a 15-day pause/reactivation cycle. This means you can pause your membership towards the end of any 15-day period and reactivate it once you have new work. For example, if you pause after 15 days of a one-month service, you have 15 remaining days to use anytime in the future. This flexibility ensures you only pay for the time you need.",{"label":91,"content":92},"How do you ensure high quality work at such a low cost?","With our team averaging over 14 years of work experience, we have developed a strong framework and tools that significantly enhance efficiency and productivity. We continuously innovate by creating new tools and processes tailored to your specific projects, ensuring we deliver high-quality work. This focus on efficiency allows us to provide top-tier services at a lower cost.",{"label":94,"content":95},"What if I want to change my project requirements after the project starts?","From our end, we ensure clear requirements and work scope through effective communication and thorough requirements analysis. However, we understand that you might change your mind or come up with new ideas during the project. We welcome any changes to the project requirements, as many times as needed, ensuring your project evolves exactly 